captions.text:
Grab your Metal Gear Ray figure and strap
yourself in with a Pokemon seatbelt...belt.
I'm Jake and this is episode 20 of Game LÜT

*Muffled Jake* Sorry let me take off this
Subzero Beanie Mask. Ok, unplug your phone

from a PSone Phone Charger and put it in an
insane Batman Batmobile Case that even shoots

the bat symbol out of the exhaust. Then grab
8 grand out of your pacman coin bank so you
can buy these Resident Evil Mansion Keys.

Keep those keys hidden behind these Marvel
Retro Comic Curtains that match with your

Avengers stained glass and these awesome superhero
family art prints by Andry Rajoelina...

If you don't plan on leaving the house put
on some fleece Batman Pajama Pants and stay

warm with your Sonic The Hedgehog Slippers
and Minecraft Enderman Hoodie, or this Skyrim

Helmet hoodie if you prefer something a little
more...rustic.

But if you're dressing to impress don't forget
Minecraft socks, and an Assassins Creed Black

Flag button up Shirt complete with Pokebow
tie or impress everyone with these insane

Blizzard game themed tshirts over at muster
brand...

For the Mrs. there's a Kingdom Hearts Keyblade
Ring, some Rupee earrings and an Arcade Dress.

And heck, why not a League of Legends necklace,
It'll go perfectly with that Umbrella Corporation
Purse.

Looking that hot must have made you parched
so take a sip out of an Aperture Science 70's

diner coffee mug and keep the table safe with
these iron man light up coaster ,or fill up

your Zelda Triforce Flask with some liquid
courage so you can battle the heat in a Nintendo

controller Bikini. Then add some style with
this matching Nintendo Controller Snapback.

But before you leave the house that fly eliminate
odor with NES controller mints and some Street

fighter Cologne so you ken smell as good as
you look.

While you're out, keep your defenses up with
a 3D Printed Team Fortress 2 turret, a Dead

Space Motorcycle Helmet and disguise your
Nintendo 3DS with a composition notebook sticker.

Or show your strength by wearing a BioShock
Infinite Handyman Heart tshirt.

At the end of the night lay your head on a
Call of Duty pillow, tuck yourself into a

Grand Theft Auto Body Bag...sleeping bag and
mark your spot with a Video Game Tombstone.

There are ones for Koopa Troopa, Dr. Light
and Link. Then dream of these video game prints
by Ayax Alarcon...

Throw in the Adventure Time towel, subscribe
to Vsauce3 for more Game LUT and melt minds
with a tie dye Ecco the Dolphin shirt.

Links to everything can be found in the description
below.
I'm Jake and, as always, thanks for watching.
